article.description: — Ben Shungu had 19 points as Vermont defeated Northern Iowa 71-57 on Thursday.
article.headline: Shungu scores 19 to lift Vermont over Northern Iowa 71-57
article.linkText: Shungu scores 19 to lift Vermont over Northern Iowa 71-57
article.story: CEDAR FALLS, Iowa -- — Ben Shungu had 19 points as Vermont defeated Northern Iowa 71-57 on Thursday. Isaiah Powell had 17 points for Vermont (1-0) in its season opener. AJ Green had 19 points for the Panthers (0-2). Noah Carter and Austin Phyfe each added 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
